Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.79,0:00:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Co to je?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Promiň, jsi v pohodě?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.58,0:00:53.85,Horimiya,,0,0,0,,{\an8\frz4.235\move(1040.001,298.667,1096,274.667)\fad(200,400)}Horimiya
